{"tid":1540003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"撤回 定 未撤 係冇分別","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:23.000Z","uid":74091,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13cc968e2ddc9b1e9f30ab4e637141649de00dd9","tid":1540003,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"林鄭6月15話暫緩果陣，所有工作已經停止，直到今日話撤回，其實而家個情況同6月15係冇分別，最多係話多左個法律基礎，但係我地係負出左好沉重既代價<br />\n雙真普選呢？幾時清算狗隊？<br />\n<br />\n而家撤回對我地既士氣有正面幫助，亦都證明我地既抗爭係有用<br />\n所以我地而家唔係要妥協接受，係要見到希望而繼續堅持<br />\n<br />\n如果一句撤回條例就令繼續抗爭既人<br />\n由200萬跌到 幾十萬既話<br />\n香港人唔配有民主<br />\n<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」"},{"pid":"6bbded4e23c2b31a82f3f84b7148723d5ae1ace5","tid":1540003,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"e50e1fb34b6c67ec0262d3521d2f940ef57a3dcc","tid":1540003,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"邊個話收貨就放圖[慎入]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=cf167111\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔好嬲，我地需要和理非曬多次馬</span><br />\n<br />\n求吓大家，暫停鑽牛角尖睇多啲評論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537499</a>"},{"pid":"864601173a6c1ef67f100593fd3cf93536460a01","tid":1540003,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"71f469b6296130e5498641d23a61cd0dea6f8742","tid":1540003,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"5be818c4bc46b80961f4d80b6c8254a8cd066c9e","tid":1540003,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":